#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!meta title=\"Printing and scanning\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!meta title=\"Impressió i escaneig\"]]\n"

#. type: Title =
#, no-wrap
msgid "Printing"
msgstr "Impressió"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"To configure a printer or manage your printing jobs, choose **Apps&nbsp;▸ "
"System Tools&nbsp;▸ Settings&nbsp;▸ Printers**."
msgstr ""
"Per configurar una impressora o gestionar els vostres treballs d'impressió, "
"seleccioneu **Aplicacions**&nbsp;▸Eines del "
"sistema&nbsp;▸Paràmetres&nbsp;▸Impressores**."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"To check the compatibility of your printer with Linux and Tails, consult the "
"[OpenPrinting database](https://openprinting.github.io/printers/) of the "
"Linux Foundation."
msgstr ""
"Per comprovar la compatibilitat de la vostra impressora amb Linux i Tails, "
"consulteu la [base de dades d'OpenPrinting](https://openprinting.github.io/"
"printers/) de la Linux Foundation."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<div class=\"tip\">\n"
"<p>To reuse the configuration of your printers across different working\n"
"sessions, turn on the [[Printers|persistent_storage/configure#printers]]\n"
"feature of the Persistent Storage.</p>\n"
"</div>\n"
msgstr ""
"<div class=\"tip\">\n"
"<p>Per reutilitzar la configuració de les vostres impressores en diferents sessions\n"
"de treball, activeu la funcionalitat [[Impressores|persistent_storage/configure#printers]]\n"
"de l'Emmagatzematge Persistent.</p>\n"
"</div>\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "Printing PDFs"
msgstr "Impressió de documents PDF"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Before printing PDFs, you can use [*BookletImposer*](https://"
"kjo.herbesfolles.org/bookletimposer/) to:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid ""
"Reduce the number of pages in a PDF by putting several pages on every sheet."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid "Produce a PDF booklet that can be folded after printing."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title =
#, no-wrap
msgid "Scanning"
msgstr "Escaneig"

#. type: Plain text
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Tails includes the [*Document Scanner*](https://gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/"
#| "simple-scan)  utility to scan documents and photos."
msgid ""
"Tails includes the [*Document Scanner*](https://apps.gnome.org//"
"SimpleScan/)  utility to scan documents and photos."
msgstr ""
"Tails inclou la utilitat [*Escàner de Documents*](https://gitlab.gnome.org/"
"GNOME/simple-scan) per escanejar documents i imatges."

#. type: Plain text
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "To start *Document Scanner*, choose **Applications**&nbsp;▸ "
#| "**Utilities**&nbsp;▸ **Document Scanner**."
msgid ""
"To open *Document Scanner*, choose **Apps&nbsp;▸ Utilities&nbsp;▸ Document "
"Scanner**."
msgstr ""
"Per iniciar l'*Escàner de Documents*, trieu **Aplicacions**&nbsp;▸ "
"**Utilitats**&nbsp;▸ **Escàner de Documents**."
